

⭐ 4. gdf loan sign — Record Digital Signatures

Command
`
gdf loan sign gdp-loan-2026-02-06-01 \
  --party facilitator \
  --signature "R.K." \
  --hash "71C4B4978007446"
`

Repeat for each signer.

What it does
- Appends signature to signatures.log.md  
- Updates metadata: signed: true  
- Locks agreement from modification  

